01:29:28.303 --> 01:29:29.940
Vlad.

01:29:29.972 --> 01:29:30.807
Momma!

01:29:33.877 --> 01:29:36.346
Vlad, you're not safe
here, they're coming.

01:29:36.379 --> 01:29:37.214
Who's coming?

01:29:38.914 --> 01:29:40.016
The night hunters.

01:29:44.053 --> 01:29:46.623
(UPBEAT MUSIC)

01:29:52.027 --> 01:29:55.865
